### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Hackathon API Test Suite — REST Client (VS Code)
### Click "Send Request" above any request to test
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

@BASE    = http://localhost:8000
@API_KEY = hackathon-secret-key-123

### ── System ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{BASE}}/health

### Swagger Docs (open in browser)
# GET {{BASE}}/docs

### ── AI Endpoints ────────────────────────────────────

### Chat — with domain context
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/chat
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Show me all offline devices and explain possible reasons",
  "include_context": true
}

###

### Chat — without context (pure LLM)
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/chat
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "What is MQTT protocol?",
  "include_context": false
}

###

### Feedback — thumbs up
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/feedback
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "response_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID",
  "rating": 1
}

###

### Feedback — thumbs down
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/feedback
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "response_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID",
  "rating": -1
}

###

### Translate
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/translate
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Device is offline. Check network connection.",
  "target_lang": "hi-IN"
}

### ── Data Endpoints ───────────────────────────────────

### List all entities
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/entities
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Get entity by ID
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/entities/dev_001
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Filter by status
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/entities/status/offline
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Get alerts
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/alerts
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Chat history
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/history
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

### ── Sarvam Direct (test your API key) ───────────────

### Direct Sarvam Chat (bypass your app)
POST https://api.sarvam.ai/v1/chat/completions
api-subscription-key: YOUR_SARVAM_KEY_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "sarvam-2b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Hello, what can you do?"}
  ]
}
